-with-a-cryptominer/</a></p>\n","last_modified":1641860409,"replies":18,"id":827461},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_large.png?m=1641783557","name":"windows","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_normal.png?m=1641783557","title":"Windows","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/windows","topics":2501,"footer":"","header":"Windows, not walls.","title_alternative":"Windows","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/e7b2/4b11/360_mini.png?m=1641783557","stars":823,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":360,"parent_node_name":"os"},"member":{"id":273091,"username":"villivateur","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/villivateur","website":"https://www.vvzero.com/","twitter":"","psn":"","github":"","btc":"","location":"","tagline":"嵌入式物联网全栈系统工程师","bio":"","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_mini.png?m=1635395897","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_normal.png?m=1635395897","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/233d/26cb/273091_large.png?m=1635395897","created":1512652845,"last_modified":1635395897},"last_reply_by":"tsanie","last_touched":1641890406,"title":"Windows server 能做什么酷酷的事情吗？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/827581","created":1641885358,"deleted":0,"content":"对于个人爱好者、极客而言，相比于 Linux ，Windows Server 能做什么好玩（ zhuang bi ）的事情吗？\r\n\r\n个人能想到的，也许做 QQ 机器人之类的会更简单？","content_rendered":"<p>对于个人爱好者、极客而言，相比于 Linux ，Windows Server 能做什么好玩（ zhuang bi ）的事情吗？</p>\n<p>个人能想到的，也许做 QQ 机器人之类的会更简单？</p>\n","last_modified":1641885358,"replies":16,"id":827581},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":47047,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m