ers","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/c20a/d4d7/12_mini.png?m=1629391393","stars":3392,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":12,"parent_node_name":"v2ex"},"member":{"id":498301,"username":"jklzhu","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/jklzhu","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/290d/4502/498301_mini.png?m=1640844180","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/290d/4502/498301_normal.png?m=1640844180","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/290d/4502/498301_large.png?m=1640844180","created":1594216876,"last_modified":1640844180},"last_reply_by":"psirnull","last_touched":1641871593,"title":"有没有抢票软件推荐","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/827503","created":1641869021,"deleted":0,"content":"同事说 bypass 会被 12306 检测到，放到低队列当中(本人也没有用过 bypass ，如果是充会员有用的话，友友也可以告诉我一下，谢谢)","content_rendered":"<p>同事说 bypass 会被 12306 检测到，放到低队列当中(本人也没有用过 bypass ，如果是充会员有用的话，友友也可以告诉我一下，谢谢)</p>\n","last_modified":1641869021,"replies":14,"id":827503},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_large.png?m=1641688451","name":"programmer","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_normal.png?m=1641688451","title":"程序员","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/programmer","topics":47050,"footer":"","header":"While code monkeys are not eating bananas, they're coding.","title_alternative":"Programmer","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/94f6/d7e0/300_mini.png?m=1641688451","stars":7660,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":300,"parent_node_name":"computer"},"member":{"id":444160,"username":"eyc","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/eyc","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/68d41c0100e42e2edb47f6c120aa5a8a?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/68d41c0100e42e2edb47f6c120aa5a8a?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/68d41c0100e42e2edb47f6c120aa5a8a?s=73&d=retro","created":1569813475,"last_modified":1641870518},"last_reply_by":"rationa1cuzz","last_touched":1641883290,"title":"裸辞一年半，要不要直接去一线城市找工作？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/827529","created":1641874850,"deleted":0,"content":"17 年毕业，在福州工作，20 年 7 月裸辞，只待过一家公司。\r\n（ 21 年出了些事，比较抑郁，最近才开始准备。）\r\n\r\n\r\n目前问题：\r\n\r\n1 、技术太渣。\r\n\r\n在前公司薪资都不到 10k ，项目基本上做的单体应用+一个很 low 的网关（用 spring cloud gateway 简单做转发），都没体会到微服务。\r\n\r\n所以最近边看八股文，边重写网关优化下，还打算去看看 SpringCloud 源码。估计下个月才能开始找工作。\r\n\r\n2 、纠结去厦门找双休公司，还是直接去一线城市。\r\n\r\n因为都说现在内卷很严重，自己看了那些面试题发现好多不会，所以打算过完年先在福州面试看看，然后直接去厦门找非外包+互联网公司（目标 13k ），待到年底，再去杭州 /北京。\r\n\r\n------\r\n\r\n\r\n不知道这个计划怎样，毕业后没出去面试过，加上紧张，我估计前期面十家都没 offer ，或者连面试机会都没有。\r\n211 毕业，看着同学们慢慢去大厂开始准备买房买车，现在有点焦虑。。\r\n\r\n希望大家能给一些建议，，然后想问下行情怎么样，特别是厦门 /杭州","content_rendered":"<p>17 年毕业，在福州工作，20 年 7 月裸辞，只待过一家公司。\n（ 21 年出了些事，比较抑郁，最近才开始准备。）</p>\n<p>目前问题：</p>\n<p>1 、技术太渣。</p>\n<p>在前公司薪资都不到 10k ，项目基本上做的单体应用+一个很 low 的网关（用 spring cloud gateway 简单做转发），都没体会到微服务。</p>\n<p>所以最近边看八股文，边重写网关优化下，还打算去看看 SpringCloud 源码。估计下个月才能开始找工作。</p>\n<p>2 、纠结去厦门找双休公司，还是直接去一线城市。</p>\n<p>因为都说现在内卷很严重，自己看了那些面试题发现好多不会，所以打算过完年先在福州面试看看，然后直接去厦门找非外包+互联网公司（目标 13k ），待到年底，再去杭州 /北京。</p>\n<hr/>\n<p>不知道这个计划怎样，毕业后没出去面试过，加上紧张，我估计前期面十家都没 offer ，或者连面试机会都没有。\n211 毕业，看着同学们慢慢去大厂开始准备买房买车，现在有点焦虑。。</p>\n<p>希望大家能给一些建议，，然后想问下行情怎么样，特别是厦门 /杭州</p>\n","last_modified":1641874850,"replies":13,"id":827529},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":17416,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2047,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":552173,"username":"Lagrangist","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/u/Lagrangist","website":null,"twitter":null,"psn":null,"github":null,"btc":null,"location":null,"tagline":null,"bio":null,"avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/84e993fa9bacb21845cfa8a300e3fad7?s=24&d=retro","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/84e993fa9bacb21845cfa8a300e3fad7?s=48&d=retro","avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/84e993fa9bacb21845cfa8a300e3fad7?s=73&d=retro","created":1627696260,"last_modified":1637928767},"last_reply_by":"syc721","last_touched":1641870417,"title":"Apple 生态全家桶适合同步的 pdf 软件有什么？","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/t/827468","created":1641862289,"deleted":0,"content":"之前一直是 ipad 用 notability ，但是在 mac 使用的时候 cpu 占用莫名其妙的高，耗电快的恐怖，遂放弃，mac 上一直是看 onedrive 备份的 notability 里面的 pdf ，而且很多 pdf 存了多份，十分麻烦，希望找一个全端同步（主要是 iPad 和 Mac ，手机太小了不方便看）的，功能不用太好，能基础的 highlight,bookmark 就行。或者说广义点，不用软件，求个全端管理阅读 pdf 的好方案。","content_rendered":"<p>之前一直是 ipad 用 notability ，但是在 mac 使用的时候 cpu 占用莫名其妙的高，耗电快的恐怖，遂放弃，mac 上一直是看 onedrive 备份的 notability 里面的 pdf ，而且很多 pdf 存了多份，十分麻烦，希望找一个全端同步（主要是 iPad 和 Mac ，手机太小了不方便看）的，功能不用太好，能基础的 highlight,bookmark 就行。或者说广义点，不用软件，求个全端管理阅读 pdf 的好方案。</p>\n","last_modified":1641862289,"replies":13,"id":827468},{"node":{"avatar_large":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_large.png?m=1630643913","name":"apple","avatar_normal":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_normal.png?m=1630643913","title":"Apple","url":"https://www.v2ex.com/go/apple","topics":17419,"footer":"","header":"设计了 <a href=\"/go/watch\">Apple Watch</a>，<a href=\"/go/ipad\">iPad</a>，<a href=\"/go/iphone\">iPhone</a>，<a href=\"/go/imac\">iMac</a> 及 <a href=\"/go/mbp\">MacBook Pro</a> 等电子产品的美国公司。","title_alternative":"Apple","avatar_mini":"https://cdn.v2ex.com/navatar/6cdd/60ea/184_mini.png?m=1630643913","stars":2047,"aliases":[],"root":false,"id":184,"parent_node_name":"hardware"},"member":{"id":384957,"username":"putaosi","url":"https://www.